# Env files — contain per-environment keys (Aptabase, server URLs).
# `.env.development` stays committed (no secrets, documents the shape).
# `.env.example` is the canonical template for contributors.
# CI regenerates `.env.production` / `.env.staging` from GitHub Secrets at build time.
.env
.env.production
.env.staging
.env.*.local

